---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Shajan Jacob
description: "Software Engineer | Hacker"
---

<section class="mb-8">
    <div class="text-justify space-y-2 line">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>I'm Shajan, a software engineer specializing in web applications development. I focus on building clean, reliable solutions while continuously exploring and <a href="#projects" class="link">experimenting</a> with <a href="#blog" class="link">new ideas</a>.</p>
        <p>When I'm not coding, I like tinkering with IoT and electronics - anything with wires or blinking lights instantly grabs my attention. I enjoy thoughtful design and creativity, whether it's selecting the right font color, making handmade crafts, or filling my space with plants. I also like capturing subtle moments through <a href="#photography" class="link">photography</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/about/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors group">
            Read more about me<span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Projects Section -->
<section class="mb-8" id="projects">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">Projects</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-1">
        {% for project in collections.projects | reverse | batch(4) | first %}
                {% include "components/project-card.njk" %}
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/projects/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors group">
            See more projects<span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-8" id="blog">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">Blog</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-1">
        {% for post in collections.blog | reverse | batch(4) | first %}
                {% include "components/blog-card.njk" %}
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/blog/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors group">
            See more blogs<span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="mt-8" id="photography">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600">Photography</h2>
    </div>
    {% set photos = collections.photos | reverse | batch(8) | first %}
    {% include "components/photo-grid.njk" %}
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/photography/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors group">
            See more photos<span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

